COMMENT ON COLUMN CLAIM_TRANSITION_REASON_TYPE.CLM_TRANS_RSN_TYP_NM IS 'A user-friendly name to describe claim transition reason type.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN CLAIM_TRANSITION_REASON_TYPE.CLM_TRANS_RSN_TYP_SYS_IND IS 'This indicator defined whether or not the claim status action is editable on-line.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN CLAIM_TRANSITION_REASON_TYPE.VOID_IND IS 'An indicator identifying whether the record has been logically deleted or not.';


