Comment on column CLAIM_WAGE_CALCULATION.CLM_WG_CALC is 'The formula that is used to calculate the wage amount';
Comment on column CLAIM_WAGE_CALCULATION.CLM_WG_CALC_DESC is 'A freeform description of the calculation';

