COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_LARGE_LOSS.PPLL_INCUR_INDM_AMT IS 'The incurred amount for indemnity on the claim';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_LARGE_LOSS.PPLL_PD_MED_AMT IS 'The amount of medical expenses paid on the claim';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_LARGE_LOSS.AUDIT_USER_ID_CREA IS 'The user identifier of the user that created this record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_LARGE_LOSS.PPLL_INCUR_MED_AMT IS 'The incurred amount for medical expenses on the claim';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_LARGE_LOSS.VOID_IND IS 'An indicator identifying whether the record has been logically deleted or not.';


