COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.PPPAGY_OVRRD_RN_IND IS 'This is an indicator specifying commission override renewal indicator for agency participation on a policy.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.PPPAGY_COMS_RT IS 'This is an override rate specified by the user to pre-empt the commission schedule rate for this participation.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.PPPAGY_COMM_RECV_IND IS 'This is an indicator specifying whether or not this agency location receives the commission for this policy period.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.PPPAGY_COMM_EFF_DTM IS 'This is the date that this agency location starts receiving commissions for the entire policy agreement.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.PPPAGY_COMM_END_DTM IS 'This is the date that this agency location stops receiving commissions for the policy agreement.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.PPPAGY_DOCM_RECV_IND IS 'This is an indicator specifying whether or not this agency location receives the documents for this policy period.';
comment on column POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_AGY.RLT_ID is 'Foreign key to RELATIONSHIP table';

