COMMENT ON TABLE POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_INS IS 'This data table captures information about insured participation on a policy for a distinct policy period.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_INS.PTCP_ID IS 'This is the primary key as well as the foreign key to the policy_period_participation table specifying the specific participation for a policy period.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_INS.PLCY_PRD_PTCP_INS_PRI_IND IS 'This is an indicator specifying if this insured participant is identified as the primary insured or not.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_INS.PLCY_PRD_PTCP_INS_CNTC_COMT IS 'This is a user entered comment to describe a contact for this insured if applicable.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_PTCP_INS.EXTRNL_NO is 'This is the Business Sequence Number used by the BWC project.';

