COMMENT ON TABLE RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE IS 'This is a code table which maps specific rating elements to unique combinations of line of business, market type, company and jurisdiction (state).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_ID IS 'This is the primary surrogate key for the table used to uniquely identify each record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.LMICJX_ID IS 'This is a foreign key to the lob_mrkt_ins_cmpy_jur_xref table specifying the unique combination of line of business, market type, company, and jurisdiction for this rating element record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_TYP_CD IS 'This is a foreign key to the rating_element_type table specifying the rating element for this record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_DSPLY_TYP_CD IS 'This is a foreign key to the rating_element_display_type table specifying the type of display for this rating element.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_EFF_DT IS 'The date that this mapping of rating element to line of business, market type, company, and jurisdiction took effect.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_END_DT IS 'The date that this mapping of rating element to line of business, market type, company, and jurisdiction is no longer in effect.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_STAT_CD IS 'The statistical reporting code for NCCI for this rating element.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_STAT_CD_CR IS 'The statistical reporting code for NCCI for this rating element if the element is specified as a credit rating element..';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_STAT_CD_DR IS 'The statistical reporting code for NCCI for this rating element if the element is specified as a debit rating element.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_DSPLY_IND IS 'An indicator specifying whether or not this rating element is displayed on the Rating Elements tab of the front end.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_USER_ENT_IND IS 'An indicator specifying whether or not this rating element can have its value entered via the frone end by the user.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_PREM_CALC_IND IS 'An indicator specifying whether or not this rating element is used in the calculation of premium.';
comment on column RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_PED_OVRRD_IND is 'This column identifies if a rating element rate is applied as of Policy Period Effective or ARD.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_VOID_IND IS 'An indicator identifying whether the record has been logically deleted or not.';
comment on column RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_ZRO_DSPLY_IND is 'This column identifies to display or not in premium calc screen when the rating element premium is zero.';
comment on column RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.CNCURNCY_ID is 'This column needs to be used only for optimistic concurrency support ONLY.';
comment on column RATING_ELEMENT_LMCJ_TYPE.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_USER_SEL_IND is 'This column identifies if the user has the ability to add the rating element manually on the rating elements screen.';


