COMMENT ON COLUMN RATING_ELEMENT_PREM_DSCNT.RT_ELEM_LMCJ_TYP_ID IS 'This is a foreign key to the rating_element_lmcj_type table specifying the unique combination of rating element, line of business, market type, company and jurisdictionn which is applicable to this premium discount program.';
