COMMENT ON COLUMN RELATIONSHIP.RLT_END_DT IS 'This date represents the date through which this relationship is valid.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RELATIONSHIP.DEP_TYP_CD IS 'This is a foreign key to dependent_type table, specifying the type of dependent. This is used only if selected relationship type is dependent.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RELATIONSHIP.RLT_NO IS 'This represents a unique alphanumeric reference number for the relationship code assigned by the carrier to identify the relationship.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN RELATIONSHIP.RLT_DAY_HRS_OP_DESC IS 'A descriptive text representing a text description for the days of the week and the associated hours that the provider is at the location.';
