COMMENT ON TABLE WC_CLASS_RATE_TIER_TYPE IS 'This is a code table which defines the types of rating tiers (used as rating elements in tiered rating) for Workers Compensation that exist in the system.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN WC_CLASS_RATE_TIER_TYPE.WC_CLS_RT_TIER_TYP_CD IS 'A unique code value to identify the specific type of rate tier.';
