COMMENT ON TABLE POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL IS 'This is a data table which capture interpolation detail information about a retrospective rating program rating element added to a policy period.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.PPRID_ID IS 'This is the primary surrogate key for the table used to uniquely identify each record.';
