COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.RRPD_ID IS 'This is a foreign key to the retrospective_rating_prog_dtl table specifying which retrospective rating program detail record that this interpolation information is associated with.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.PPRID_100_PCT_PREM_AMT IS 'The 100 percent premium amount associated to the retrospective rating program.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.PPRID_50_BSC_PREM_FCTR IS 'The 50 percent basic premium factor associated to the retrospective rating program.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.PPRID_150_BSC_PREM_FCTR IS 'The 150 percent basic premium factor associated to the retrospective rating program.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.AUDIT_USER_ID_CREA IS 'The user identifier of the user that created this record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.AUDIT_USER_CREA_DTM IS 'Date and time record was created.  Used for audit purposes.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.AUDIT_USER_ID_UPDT IS 'The user identifier of the user that updated this record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.AUDIT_USER_UPDT_DTM IS 'Date and time record was updated.  Used for audit purposes.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.VOID_IND IS 'An indicator identifying whether the record has been logically deleted or not.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN POLICY_PERIOD_RTSP_INTRPL_DTL.PPRID_100_PCT_PREM_IND IS 'retrieve 100 percent premium amount Indicator.';

