COMMENT ON COLUMN CLAIM_SUMMARY.CS_NCCI_POB_TYP_NM IS 'This is the column which contains NCCI primary part of the body type name.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN CLAIM_SUMMARY.VOID_IND IS 'Indicates whether the record is voided';
COMMENT ON COLUMN CLAIM_SUMMARY.CS_CLM_NO IS 'Represents the number used to identify the claim.';
