COMMENT ON COLUMN DISTRIBUTION_METHOD_TYPE.DISTR_METH_TYP_NM IS 'Name that describes the Payment Distribution Method.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN DISTRIBUTION_METHOD_TYPE.VOID_IND IS 'An indicator identifying whether the record has been logically deleted or not.';


